data.description: 5770 Cactus Circle Spring Hill, FL 34606 - Welcome to your dream home at 5770 Cactus Circle in the charming town of Spring Hill, FL. This stunning corner lot property boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and 1,760 square feet of living space. As you pull into the driveway, you'll immediately notice the well maintained yard, long driveway, and 2-car attached garage with a new remote controlled screen, providing ample space for your vehicles and storage needs.Step inside and be greeted by a beautifully remodeled kitchen and bathrooms, featuring granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and modern fixtures. The open floor plan allows for easy flow between the kitchen, dining area, and living room, making it perfect for entertaining guests or spending quality time with family.The bedrooms are spacious and offer plenty of natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The master bedroom boasts an en-suite bathroom, providing a private oasis for relaxation. The entire home is adorned with elegant plantation shutters, adding a touch of sophistication to each room.But the features don't stop there. This property also includes a bonus room off of the garage, currently used as an office, providing a separate space for work or hobbies. And for those hot summer days, cool off in the 18x36 above ground pool, perfect for hosting pool parties or simply lounging in the sun.Located in a desirable neighborhood, this home offers the perfect balance of privacy and community. Don't miss your chance to make this house your forever home. Schedule a showing today and see for yourself all that 5770 Cactus Circle has to offer.
